'''Adidas Beau Jeu'''是[[2016年欧洲足球锦标赛|2016年欧洲足球锦标赛]]的官方比赛用球。法语“Beau Jeu”意为“完美的比赛”（{{lang|en|Beautiful Game}}）。该球由[[阿迪达斯|阿迪达斯]]设计，于2015年11月12日由法国国家队前队员[[齐内丁·齐达内|齐内丁·齐达内]]公布<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/euro-2016/11990580/Adidas-unveils-official-match-ball-for-Euro-2016.html |title=Adidas unveils official match ball for Euro 2016 |accessdate=2016-05-27 |archive-date=2017-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427211908/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/euro-2016/11990580/Adidas-unveils-official-match-ball-for-Euro-2016.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.footyheadlines.com/2015/06/adidas-euro-2016-ball.html |title=Adidas Beau Jeu Euro 2016 Ball Released |accessdate=2016-05-27 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604225206/http://www.footyheadlines.com/2015/06/adidas-euro-2016-ball.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，采用[[巴西荣耀|巴西荣耀]]的元素<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.ie/sport/soccer/international-soccer/here-is-the-ball-we-hope-ireland-are-kicking-in-france-next-june-34194068.html |title=Here is the ball we hope Ireland are kicking in France next June |accessdate=2016-05-27 |archive-date=2017-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507173115/http://www.independent.ie/sport/soccer/international-soccer/here-is-the-ball-we-hope-ireland-are-kicking-in-france-next-june-34194068.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。蓝色线条和红色线条交相辉映，每一行印有构成字母“EURO”和数字“2016”的字样。

